503
00:29:15,203 --> 00:29:17,672
Kemudian pergilah ke Seoul.

504
00:29:18,006 --> 00:29:19,541
Di sana ada banyak sekali laki-laki.

505
00:29:19,541 --> 00:29:21,443
Jangan bertingkah konyol.

506
